{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01D1TWbs8S8VL3oYETCL1bM6","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All tests pass across the entire project.\n\n## Summary\n\n**Root cause:** The DSL parser stores prompt/script config values with `file(\"path\")` wrapper syntax (e.g., `file(\".cloche/prompts/implement.md\")`), but `handleAPIStepContent` was treating these values as raw file paths, so `os.ReadFile` would fail on a path like `file(\".cloche/prompts/implement.md\")`.\n\n**Fix:** Added a `resolveFileRef()` helper function that strips the `file(\"...\")` wrapper before reading the file. Applied it to all three config types (`prompt`, `command`, `script`) in `handleAPIStepContent`.\n\n**Files changed:**\n- `internal/adapters/web/handler.go` — Updated `handleAPIStepContent` to use `resolveFileRef()` and added the helper function\n- `internal/adapters/web/handler_test.go` — Added `TestResolveFileRef` (unit test for the helper) and `TestAPIStepContent_FileRef` (integration test for the endpoint)\n\nCLOCHE_RESULT:success"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":645,"cache_read_input_tokens":45811,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":645},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"568632a5-c6f9-4716-acd6-dad26849e95f","uuid":"e6af0b6d-5255-42f3-ab05-d007dc5164ac"}
{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":212574,"duration_api_ms":170865,"num_turns":39,"result":"All tests pass across the entire project.\n\n## Summary\n\n**Root cause:** The DSL parser stores prompt/script config values with `file(\"path\")` wrapper syntax (e.g., `file(\".cloche/prompts/implement.md\")`), but `handleAPIStepContent` was treating these values as raw file paths, so `os.ReadFile` would fail on a path like `file(\".cloche/prompts/implement.md\")`.\n\n**Fix:** Added a `resolveFileRef()` helper function that strips the `file(\"...\")` wrapper before reading the file. Applied it to all three config types (`prompt`, `command`, `script`) in `handleAPIStepContent`.\n\n**Files changed:**\n- `internal/adapters/web/handler.go` — Updated `handleAPIStepContent` to use `resolveFileRef()` and added the helper function\n- `internal/adapters/web/handler_test.go` — Added `TestResolveFileRef` (unit test for the helper) and `TestAPIStepContent_FileRef` (integration test for the endpoint)\n\nCLOCHE_RESULT:success","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"568632a5-c6f9-4716-acd6-dad26849e95f","total_cost_usd":1.0117926499999998,"usage":{"input_tokens":37,"cache_creation_input_tokens":33579,"cache_read_input_tokens":1125842,"output_tokens":6834,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":33579,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-opus-4-6":{"inputTokens":37,"outputTokens":6834,"cacheReadInputTokens":1125842,"cacheCreationInputTokens":33579,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.9438247499999999,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000},"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001":{"inputTokens":31,"outputTokens":1480,"cacheReadInputTokens":94919,"cacheCreationInputTokens":40836,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.0679679,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000}},"permission_denials":[],"fast_mod